data.title: Dancing With the Stars' Peta Murgatroyd and Maksim Chmerkovskiy Welcome Their First Child
data.meta_description: Shai Aleksander Chmerkovskiy was born Wednesday morning
data.text:
It's a Dancing baby boy!

Dancing with the Starspro Peta Murgatroyd gave birth to her first child with her fianc√©, former Dancing pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy, Wednesday morning. The new dad announced that Shai Aleksander Chmerkovskiy was born early on Wednesday.

Murgatroyd and Chmerkovskiy met in 2009 when they both danced in a Broadway production of Burn the Floor and got engaged in 2015. Chmerkovskiy said in October that he's leaving the show to be a full-time dad. It's the first child for both.

They're wise to not hyphenate the baby's name. Shai Aleksander Chmerkovskiy-Murgatroyd would be too much.
